---
permalink: /
title: "Plasticmind = Jesse Gardner"
description: "A technologist who cares about empowering people with technology."
section: "home"
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Home
  title: Home
  order: 1
"changefreq": "weekly"
"priority": "1.0"
---

{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block content %}

<article class="c-article c-article--home">
  <div class="l-container--lg">

    <div class="c-bio">
      <img src="/assets/i/jesse-gardner.jpg" alt="Jesse Gardner" class="c-bio__photo">
      <div class="c-bio__text">
        <h1 class="c-heading c-heading--lg">Hi, I'm Jesse!</h1>
        <p class="c-subtitle">I care a lot about empowering people with technology.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="c-article__body">
      <p>I've spent 25 years at the intersection of design and engineering. I currently direct the Accessibility and Design Systems teams for <a href="https://designsystem.ny.gov">New York State</a>, where I'm exploring how design systems can serve as AI infrastructure. I also write about bridging design and engineering at <a href="https://practicaldesignsystems.com">Practical Design Systems</a>.</p>
    </div>

    {% include "partials/end-mark.njk" %}

  </div>
</article>

<section class="c-section">
  <div class="l-container--lg">
    <h2 class="c-heading c-heading--md">Selected Entries</h2>
    <ul class="c-home-list">
      {% for item in homeWriting %}
        <li class="c-home-list__item">
          <a href="{{ item.url }}" class="c-home-list__link"{% if item.url.startsWith('http') %} rel="external"{% endif %}>
            <span class="c-home-list__title">{{ item.title }}</span>
            <span class="c-home-list__meta">
              <span class="c-home-list__source">{{ item.publication }}</span>
              <span class="c-home-list__year">{{ item.year }}</span>
            </span>
          </a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    <a href="/journal/" class="c-link--more">More in the journal &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="c-section">
  <div class="l-container--lg">
    <h2 class="c-heading c-heading--md">Talks & Interviews</h2>
    <ul class="c-home-list">
      {% for item in homeTalks %}
        <li class="c-home-list__item">
          <a href="{{ item.url }}" class="c-home-list__link" rel="external">
            <span class="c-home-list__title">{{ item.title }}</span>
            <span class="c-home-list__meta">
              <span class="c-home-list__source">{{ item.venue }}</span>
              <span class="c-home-list__year">{{ item.year }}</span>
            </span>
          </a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="c-section">
  <div class="l-container--lg">
    <h2 class="c-heading c-heading--md">Awards</h2>
    <ul class="c-home-list">
      {% for item in homeAwards %}
        <li class="c-home-list__item">
          {% if item.url %}
            <a href="{{ item.url }}" class="c-home-list__link" rel="external">
              <span class="c-home-list__title">{{ item.title }}</span>
              <span class="c-home-list__meta">
                <span class="c-home-list__source">{{ item.org }}</span>
                <span class="c-home-list__year">{{ item.year }}</span>
              </span>
            </a>
          {% else %}
            <span class="c-home-list__link">
              <span class="c-home-list__title">{{ item.title }}</span>
              <span class="c-home-list__meta">
                <span class="c-home-list__source">{{ item.org }}</span>
                <span class="c-home-list__year">{{ item.year }}</span>
              </span>
            </span>
          {% endif %}
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="c-section">
  <div class="l-container--lg">
    <h2 class="c-heading c-heading--md">Projects</h2>
    <ul class="c-home-list c-home-list--projects">
      {% for item in homeProjects %}
        <li class="c-home-list__item">
          <a href="{{ item.url }}" class="c-home-list__link" rel="external">
            <span class="c-home-list__title">{{ item.title }}</span>
            <span class="c-home-list__meta">
              <span class="c-home-list__source">{{ item.description }}</span>
            </span>
          </a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="c-section c-section--testimonials">
  <div class="l-container--lg">
    <h2 class="c-heading c-heading--md">People I've Helped</h2>
    <div class="c-testimonials" id="js-testimonials">
      {# Server-renders all testimonials; JS randomly shows 2 on load #}
      {% for item in homeTestimonials %}
        <blockquote class="c-testimonial" data-testimonial>
          <p class="c-testimonial__quote">{{ item.quote }}</p>
          <footer class="c-testimonial__cite">— {% if item.link %}<a href="{{ item.link }}" rel="external">{{ item.name }}</a>{% else %}{{ item.name }}{% endif %}{% if item.organization %}, {{ item.organization }}{% endif %}</footer>
        </blockquote>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<aside class="c-home-coda">
  <div class="l-container--lg">
    <p class="c-home-coda__text">Two decades of thinking out loud on the internet.</p>
    <a href="/archives/" class="c-home-coda__link">Explore the archives &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</aside>

{% endblock %}

{% block scripts %}
  <script src="/assets/js/testimonials.js"></script>
{% endblock %}
